# Brighter Minds Teaching and Vocational College (BMTVC)

Welcome to the official website repository for **Brighter Minds Teaching and Vocational College**.  
Our mission is to empower learners with practical skills, vocational training, and academic excellence to prepare them for a brighter future.  

🌐 **Live Website:** [Brighter Minds College Website](https://yourusername.github.io/brighter-minds-college/)  
(Replace `yourusername` with your actual GitHub username)

---

## 📚 Courses Offered
- Hospitality & Management  
- Baking Technology  
- Nutrition  
- Barista Training  
- Computer Training  
- Caregiver Studies  
- Hair & Beauty  

---

## ✨ Features
- 🎨 Modern, responsive design with animated backgrounds  
- 📝 Admission form for new students  
- 🤖 Interactive chatbot assistant for instant Q&A  
- 📱 Mobile-friendly and accessible across all devices  

---

## 📍 Branches
- **Main Branch:** Banana, Kiambu  
- **Branch:** Kayole, Nairobi  

